      "markdown": "# ‚è≠Ô∏è C5 ‚Äî Future / Conditional Irregular Stems\n\n**Goal:** Form futuro & condicional with the correct **irregular stems** and shared endings.\n\n---\n\n## üîß Endings (regular for all verbs)\n- **Futuro:** *infinitive +* **√©, √°s, √°, emos, √©is, √°n**  \n- **Condicional:** *infinitive +* **√≠a, √≠as, √≠a, √≠amos, √≠ais, √≠an**\n\nIrregulars replace the infinitive with a **special stem**, then add the same endings.\n\n---\n\n## üìã Ra√≠ces irregulares\n- **decir** ‚Äî ra√≠z **dir-** ¬∑ futuro (yo) **dir√©** ¬∑ condicional (yo) **dir√≠a**\n- **hacer** ‚Äî ra√≠z **har-** ¬∑ futuro (yo) **har√©** ¬∑ condicional (yo) **har√≠a**\n- **poder** ‚Äî ra√≠z **podr-** ¬∑ futuro (yo) **podr√©** ¬∑ condicional (yo) **podr√≠a**\n- **poner** ‚Äî ra√≠z **pondr-** ¬∑ futuro (yo) **pondr√©** ¬∑ condicional (yo) **pondr√≠a**\n- **salir** ‚Äî ra√≠z **saldr-** ¬∑ futuro (yo) **saldr√©** ¬∑ condicional (yo) **saldr√≠a**\n- **tener** ‚Äî ra√≠z **tendr-** ¬∑ futuro (yo) **tendr√©** ¬∑ condicional (yo) **tendr√≠a**\n- **venir** ‚Äî ra√≠z **vendr-** ¬∑ futuro (yo) **vendr√©** ¬∑ condicional (yo) **vendr√≠a**\n- **querer** ‚Äî ra√≠z **querr-** ¬∑ futuro (yo) **querr√©** ¬∑ condicional (yo) **querr√≠a**\n- **saber** ‚Äî ra√≠z **sabr-** ¬∑ futuro (yo) **sabr√©** ¬∑ condicional (yo) **sabr√≠a**\n- **haber** ‚Äî ra√≠z **habr-** ¬∑ futuro (yo) **habr√©** (habr√° 3sg impersonal) ¬∑ condicional (yo) **habr√≠a**\n- **caber** ‚Äî ra√≠z **cabr-** ¬∑ futuro (yo) **cabr√©** ¬∑ condicional (yo) **cabr√≠a**\n- **valer** ‚Äî ra√≠z **valdr-** ¬∑ futuro (yo) **valdr√©** ¬∑ condicional (yo) **valdr√≠a**\n\n\n> üìù **Why:** Future/conditional share endings. Only the **stem** changes ‚Üí memorize the dozen stems once.\n",
